{
  "stem": "10272.6",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was so tired that I fall-- sitting in this hay, it felt so good that I dozed off.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I dozed off.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "All of a sudden, they wake me up-- shh!-- because one of the guys had to go out-- up the roof and watch.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "If somebody's coming, he have to tell us to cover ourselves.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So he'd give us a, a sign.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They are coming.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Then we heard steps and, and, and, and, and noises and, and German voices speaking German.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the guy came down.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he went away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he told us about nine-- a group of nine soldiers with anti-tank weapons were coming towards us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they stopped.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they were talking.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then they moved further away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So I dozed off again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And around 2, 3 o'clock in the morning, I woke up to a terrible noise, like, you know, when it's lightning and, and thundering storm with an earthquake together.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Both the earthquake-- the earth was shaking.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Everything was shaking.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Shells were exploding next to our-- next to our barn.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We heard even the-- we heard the-- and, and, and, and bullets are fleeing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We heard the bullets flee through our ears.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And we, we are hiding in this-- in the-- inside in the barn.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And we were waiting any minute a shell should fall on our head and destroy-- and, and then kill us all.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So this lasted for about till 6 o'clock in the morning-- three or four hours, this battle.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We heard aircraft flying and, and shooting, and artillery shooting, and tanks, and everything.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And then all of a sudden, it was-- quiet down.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We had only-- we had only automatic fire.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So we decided to send out somebody to look out and see what is going on.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
